  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine whether local infiltration analgesia (LIA) with
      Ropivacaine and adrenaline is effective in the treatment of postoperative pain after major
      spine surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
